Trade/Device Name(s): Dimension® CardioPhase® high sensitivity C-reactive protein Calibrator
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Dimension® clinical chemistry system with heterogeneous immunoassay module
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Dimension CardioPhase high sensitivity C-reactive protein Calibrator (CCRP Calibrator - RC434) for calibration of CRP assays on the Dimension clinical chemistry system.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended to calibrate the Dimension CardioPhase high sensitivity C-reactive protein method for the Dimension clinical chemistry system with the heterogeneous immunoassay module.
